org.loboevolution.apache.xpath.objects

Class XNumber

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.loboevolution.apache.xpath.Expression
      • org.loboevolution.apache.xpath.objects.XObject
        • org.loboevolution.apache.xpath.objects.XNumber
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ExpressionNode, XPathVisitable, SourceLocator

    public class XNumber
extends XObject
    This class represents an XPath number, and is capable of converting the number to other types, such as a string.
